oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Photo from 1950 Jubilee Party
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: African Americans; Cotton Makers' Jubilee; social life;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photo from the 1950 Jubilee Party showing the royal court. Included in this photo are Gracie Brown, Melvin Conley, Cornelia Crenshaw, Elmer Henderson, Patricia Cummings Hooks, Betty Johnson, George W. Lee, Mary Dell Moore, Bill Nabors, Joe Lee Nelson, Orin Pickett, Lee Eleanor Reed, Mary Roberts, and Ethyl Venson.
